        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I agree that this has drawbacks, although I don't see this idea bend the rules too much.\n\nIt is, however, not adding something that cannot currently be done. Users could always type their loop variables or assignment target variables accordingly. This adds mostly syntactic sugar.\n\nI'll leave this ticket open as a place for discussion and future consideration, but do not consider it something that we should pursue in the near future.",
